00:10:52.490 --> 00:10:55.100 align:middle line:84%
is the descendant
of voyagers who

00:10:55.100 --> 00:10:57.920 align:middle line:84%
came to the Western
coast of North America.

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:00.740 align:middle line:90%
>> Hold that thought.

